\f2\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf2 \cb3 \'a0Inside the silos, the ramped walkway opens up into a series of radial platforms \'96 allowing the public to intertwine above and below the industrial programs now taking place. Identifying the existing columns and roof truss as the primary structural elements \'96 the contemporary platforms are hung off of the top, freeing up the spaces below.
\fs29\fsmilli14667  
\fs26\fsmilli13333 The architecture is coded with the intention for these two demographics to interact, exposing the traversing public to the industrial performances that are unveiled along the way.\
